Subject: [FD] SPA Cart CMS - Multiple SQL Injection Web Vulnerabilities

Document Title:
===============
SPA Cart CMS - Multiple SQL Injection Web Vulnerabilities


References (Source):
====================
https://www.vulnerability-lab.com/get_content.php?id=2304


Release Date:
=============
2021-10-18


