Vulnerability Class:
====================
Script Code Injection


Current Estimated Price:
========================
1.000€ - 2.000€


Product & Service Introduction:
===============================
SPA-Cart - Single Page Application. Fully featured eCommerce CMS platform. Very fast ajaxfied pages.

(Copy of the Homepage: https://spa-cart.com/ )


Abstract Advisory Information:
==============================
The vulnerability laboratory core research team discovered a remote sql-injection web vulnerability in the SPA Cart CMS (v2021) web-application.


Affected Product(s):
====================
olegkhorev
Product: SPA Cart CMS (v2021) - Content Management System (Web-Application)


Vulnerability Disclosure Timeline:
==================================
